{"word":"σκορακίζω","slug":"σκορακίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκορακίζω</b></el> <el>(σκορᾰκίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἐς κόρακας</el>, <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:κόραξ'><el>κόραξ</el></a>\n<p/><i>to dismiss contemptuously</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be treated contemptuously</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}